  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/636e241f1c04ea1f23923f3381a3c87f.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/6315e75f76ee139b412e6ef87e638b74.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/6315e75f76ee139b412e6ef87e638b74.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gate Guardian is a fantasy roguelite in the horde survival genre with the ability to create your own spells.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/2eabd4484dd32ee9f93f6e9acfbebb8c.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/17ccdae76b9e0b77803bcebad51ab89b.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/17ccdae76b9e0b77803bcebad51ab89b.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather an arsenal of skills and spells that better suit your play style. Enhance the power of your abilities with <strong>passive skills</strong> and <strong>upgrades</strong>. Use <strong>evolutions</strong> to change the spell up to <strong>three times</strong>. For example:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a fire projectile with periodic damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add a fan of magic projectiles instead of just one</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add periodic explosions to the projectile</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/98b03bf9c1842bc4fd4024e6821807a1.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/f7b8d81820b5d18d6018b741c700ce52.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/f7b8d81820b5d18d6018b741c700ce52.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The variation in spell creation will allow you to create builds that spit on balance. Destroy enemies faster than they appear. Fill the screen with explosions and smash the FPS counter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/2322df6de1ec6d6a2ed7a45fc020cc6a.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/ec41a5eea51a9acd7fbd9f1fea3da397.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/ec41a5eea51a9acd7fbd9f1fea3da397.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hordes of undead are on their way, and there are some extremely dangerous opponents among them. Try to delay the moment of imminent end, because you are the only barrier defending life. Survive Death!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/636e241f1c04ea1f23923f3381a3c87f.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/6315e75f76ee139b412e6ef87e638b74.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/6315e75f76ee139b412e6ef87e638b74.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gate Guardian is a fantasy roguelite in the horde survival genre with the ability to create your own spells.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/2eabd4484dd32ee9f93f6e9acfbebb8c.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/17ccdae76b9e0b77803bcebad51ab89b.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/17ccdae76b9e0b77803bcebad51ab89b.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather an arsenal of skills and spells that better suit your play style. Enhance the power of your abilities with <strong>passive skills</strong> and <strong>upgrades</strong>. Use <strong>evolutions</strong> to change the spell up to <strong>three times</strong>. For example:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a fire projectile with periodic damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add a fan of magic projectiles instead of just one</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add periodic explosions to the projectile</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/98b03bf9c1842bc4fd4024e6821807a1.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/f7b8d81820b5d18d6018b741c700ce52.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/f7b8d81820b5d18d6018b741c700ce52.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The variation in spell creation will allow you to create builds that spit on balance. Destroy enemies faster than they appear. Fill the screen with explosions and smash the FPS counter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/2322df6de1ec6d6a2ed7a45fc020cc6a.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/ec41a5eea51a9acd7fbd9f1fea3da397.poster.avif?t=1774425211\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975040/extras/ec41a5eea51a9acd7fbd9f1fea3da397.webm?t=1774425211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hordes of undead are on their way, and there are some extremely dangerous opponents among them. Try to delay the moment of imminent end, because you are the only barrier defending life. Survive Death!</p>",
